short_summary: Advance contract award notice. The Department of Natural Resources Canada (NRCan) has a requirement to conduct a study on the use of high-resolution borehole profiling techniques to investigate high-heat producing intrusions, faults, and geothermal gradients associated with some mineral deposits.
description: Study on high-resolution borehole profiling techniques and their application in mineral resources. The study will aim to develop a comprehensive understanding of the geological context and geological conditions that influence the presence of high-heat producing intrusions, faults, and geothermal gradients.,
tags: High-heat producing intrusions, faults, and geothermal gradients and mineral deposits.
